  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large wok or frying pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the lemongrass and galangal and sauté until fragrant.",
    "Add the mushrooms and cook until they release their liquid and start to brown.",
    "Add the Tom Yum paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the coconut milk, fish sauce, soy sauce, and lime juice. Stir well to combine.",
    "Add the sea bass fillets and fish balls to the wok or frying pan.",
    "Cook for 3-4 minutes or until the fish is cooked through.",
    "Stir in the honey and Thai basil leaves.",
    "Season with more fish sauce or lime juice if necessary.",
    "Serve hot and garnish with additional Thai basil leaves if desired.",
    "Serve with steamed rice or noodles if preferred.",
    "Enjoy!"
